[0,"o","$ vivarium help\n"]
[0.08,"o","      .-\"\"\"-.\n   .-'  .-.  '-.\n  /  .-(   )-.  \\\n __      __ _____ __      __    _     ____  ___  _   _  __  __\n \\ \\    / /|_   _|\\ \\    / /   / \\   |  _ \\|_ _|| | | ||  \\/  |\n  \\ \\  / /   | |   \\ \\  / /   / _ \\  | |_) || | | | | || |\\/| |\n   \\ \\/ /    | |    \\ \\/ /   / ___ \\ |  _ < | | | |_| || |  | |\n    \\__/    |____|   \\__/   /_/   \\_\\|_| \\_\\___| \\___/ |_|  |_|\n            VIVARIUM // local memory // world culture\n\nVivarium Agent\n--------------\n\nFirst run\n  [1] Set up Vivarium\n      vivarium --setup\n  [2] Run the local agent\n      vivarium local run\n  [3] Open the dashboard\n      vivarium dashboard\n  [4] Verify the Mac daemon\n      vivarium daemon smoke\n  [5] Keep moving\n      vivarium status\n      vivarium help\n      vivarium update\n\nCommands\n  vivarium --setup                                       Set up local memory and show the localhost gateway path.\n  vivarium start                                         Start guided local setup with the starter pack.\n  vivarium local                                         Create the default local agent and starter memory.\n  vivarium local run                                     Run the local agent offline with the built-in provider.\n  vivarium dashboard                                     Show the local daemon gateway URL.\n  vivarium onboard                                       Run local onboarding with the starter pack.\n  vivarium setup live                                    Run the full live setup wizard with private default files.\n  vivarium onboard live                                  Alias for the live setup wizard.\n  vivarium setup                                         Initialize local state and starter world.\n  vivarium status                                        Show local and production readiness status.\n  vivarium doctor                                        Run offline readiness checks.\n  vivarium connect                                       Show provider signup and live setup guidance.\n  vivarium model                                         Show provider profile readiness.\n  vivarium tools                                         Show external toolsets and safety policy posture.\n  vivarium connect wizard                                Custom-path live setup for advanced operators.\n  vivarium connect init                                  Lower-level setup file creation for custom paths.\n  vivarium connect signup                                Show account links and the local value map.\n  vivarium connect fill                                  Fill common live setup values, paths, and names by friendly labels.\n  vivarium connect setup --confirm-write                 Write live setup files after reviewing readiness.\n  vivarium connect smoke                                 Run guided provider and credential smoke checks.\n  vivarium proof init                                    Create the v1 evidence manifest from the setup file.\n  vivarium proof                                         Review the v1 evidence checklist without raw manifest keys.\n  vivarium daemon smoke                                  Verify the Mac LaunchAgent daemon.\n  vivarium launch handoff                                Show the Mac install command and production boundary.\n  vivarium update                                        Pull the latest agent and refresh dependencies.\n  vivarium world search --domain coding --query <query>  Search world knowledge.\n  vivarium help                                          Show this command guide.\n"]
[0.2,"o","$ vivarium --setup --domain coding --world-root <demo-world> --state-path <demo-state.db> --live-env-path <demo-live-readiness.local.env>\n"]
[0.28,"o","      .-\"\"\"-.\n   .-'  .-.  '-.\n  /  .-(   )-.  \\\n __      __ _____ __      __    _     ____  ___  _   _  __  __\n \\ \\    / /|_   _|\\ \\    / /   / \\   |  _ \\|_ _|| | | ||  \\/  |\n  \\ \\  / /   | |   \\ \\  / /   / _ \\  | |_) || | | | | || |\\/| |\n   \\ \\/ /    | |    \\ \\/ /   / ___ \\ |  _ < | | | |_| || |  | |\n    \\__/    |____|   \\__/   /_/   \\_\\|_| \\_\\___| \\___/ |_|  |_|\n            VIVARIUM // local memory // world culture\n\nVivarium Setup\n--------------\nAgent: local-agent\nLocal state initialized: <demo-state.db>\nDomain: coding\nStarter skills: 22\nStarter traces: 4\nLocal setup is ready now.\nLive readiness: staged for later\nReadiness file: <demo-live-readiness.local.env>\nPermissions: 0600\nDashboard: http://127.0.0.1:8787\nStatus JSON: http://127.0.0.1:8787/status\n\nNext commands:\n  [1] Run the local agent\n      vivarium local run --domain coding --state-path <demo-state.db> --world-root <demo-world> --live-env-path <demo-live-readiness.local.env>\n  [2] Open the dashboard\n      vivarium dashboard\n  [3] Verify the Mac daemon\n      vivarium daemon smoke\n  [4] Keep moving\n      vivarium status\n      vivarium tools\n      vivarium help\n      vivarium update\n\n"]
